data.name: rtbInstruct.Text
data.value: To roll the dice say roll. To quit the game say quit game. To restart the game say restart game. Avatars can be chosen by their name, the names are beaver, walrus, ladybug and bird. Bird and Ladybug can be picked for player one. To pick a computer or player as player two. Say computer or player. Deluxe, standard and Harry Potter will pick the map. The game tells you your roll, position and place on the board. As well as who wins. Good luck
